# Week 5 Task 1 — YOLO Labeling and Dataset Preparation

## Objective
Preparing a labeled dataset for YOLO object detection training using Label Studio.

## Task Performed
- Installed Label Studio in virtual environment
- Extracted frames from video using ffmpeg
- Split dataset into train, validation, and test folders
- Annotated bottles using bounding boxes
- Exported labels in YOLO format
- Created dataset.yaml, train.txt, and val.txt

## Dataset Details
- Object Class: Bottle
- Training Images: 100
- Validation Images: 40
- Test Images: Remaining images

## Tools Used
- FFmpeg
- Label Studio
- YOLO Dataset Format

## Folder Structure

dataset/
├── images/
│   ├── train/
│   ├── val/
│   └── test/
│
├── labels/
│   ├── train/
│   └── val/
│
├── dataset.yaml
├── train.txt
└── val.txt

## Outcome
Successfully created a YOLO-compatible labeled dataset ready for training.
